Bravo to the police for the  arrest of  suspects  in connection with the   robbery at Menzi Primary School in Tsakane, Ekurhuleni. More than 200 computer equipment, a plasma TV and other electronic goods were stolen from the school which was officially opened only last week. We salute the police for their sterling work in apprehending the suspects and members of the public for tipping off the police on the suspects' hide out.